msgid ""
"**`@perryts/tursodb`** — Turso (libSQL fork) database client. See [PerryTS/"
"tursodb-bindings](https://github.com/PerryTS/tursodb-bindings)."
msgstr "**`@perryts/tursodb`** — Client cơ sở dữ liệu Turso (nhánh libSQL). Xem [PerryTS/tursodb-bindings](https://github.com/PerryTS/tursodb-bindings)."

