msgid ""
"Securely store sensitive data like tokens, passwords, and API keys using the "
"platform's secure storage. Every snippet below is excerpted from [`docs/"
"examples/system/snippets.ts`](../../examples/system/snippets.ts) — CI links "
"it on every PR."
